        "product_description": {
            "value": "Bring fun, confidence, and style to every hair-care routine with this Barbie Paddle Hair Brush. Designed in a vibrant pink color and featuring a bold graphic of three iconic Barbie dolls, this detangling brush adds a playful touch to any hair accessories collection. The wide paddle design gently glides through knots, making it perfect for daily brushing on all hair types—straight, wavy, curly, thick, or fine.\r\n\r\nMade with high-quality, durable, and child-friendly materials, this Barbie hairbrush delivers a smooth, tug-free experience that kids and adults will enjoy. Its comfortable grip and flat back allow for easy handling, helping little ones learn healthy hair-care habits. Ideal as a stocking stuffer, party favor, goodie-bag item, or prize for Barbie-themed events. Recommended for ages 3 and up, this brush is a must-have accessory for every Barbie fan.",
